pecially since they may share the same JVM. I should check if `FileSystem.newInstanceLocal(configuration)` exists to avoid cache problems. There could be risks with closing a cached filesystem.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Investigating FSDataInputStream**\\n\\nI'm looking into `FSDataInputStream`, which extends `DataInputStream` and implements several interfaces. It has a method `readFully(byte[])`, which is significant. I wonder about using `assertThat(actual).isEqualTo(expected)` for byte arrays in AssertJ—does it compare contents properly? It appears that `assertThat(byte[])` returns an `AbstractByteArrayAssert`, which should support that, but existing examples use `containsExactly`. I'm also considering naming conventions and potential conflicts with `java.nio.file.Path`. Finally, just confirming we haven't run any tests yet, per instructions!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Updated `tests/src/org.apache.hadoop/hadoop-client-api/3.3.1/src/test/java/org_apache_hadoop/hadoop_client_api/Hadoop_client_apiTest.java`.\n\nWhat I found already covered:\n- `Configuration` XML and typed value parsing\n- `StorageSize`, `Path`, and `FsPermission`\n- Hadoop writable types and comparators\n- Bloom filters and hash APIs\n- Metrics registry snapshots\n- `ReflectionUtils` configured object creation\n- `ToolRunner` generic option parsing\n- YARN records and token identifier state\n\nNew functional feature added:\n- Local Hadoop `FileSystem` operations via public API:\n  - Creates a local filesystem-backed directory\n  - Writes data through `FSDataOutputStream`\n  - Reads it back through `FSDataInputStream`\n  - Verifies `FileStatus`\n  - Lists directory contents\n  - Renames the file\n  - Deletes the directory recursively\n  - Cleans up the temporary directory with bounded local filesystem cleanup\n\nNo existing test logic was changed, and no build files or metadata/config resources were modified. I did not run tests, per the workflow constraints.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c063f8bbf3950130169fec446b82081a3a9f79648d6fe0936\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1468, "output": 715, "cacheRead": 20992, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23175, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778304060631, "responseId": "resp_0c063f8bbf3950130169fec43d12dc81a3b127fabbadf857e1"}}
